members.member:

Register a collision monitor to recieve collision events on an object.

The HierarchyPath for the object to rotate.
/// Type of hit (0 hit, 1 overlap, 2 overlapend)
The timeout in seconds to wait for a response that the request was processed by the GameDriver agent.
 String returned is the event identifier
api.RegisterUnrealCollisionMonitor("//*[@name='Cylinder']");
